snippet.title: Niharika Konidela Opens Up ||  Nikhil Vijayendra Simha || Nikhil Tho Naatakalu 2.O
snippet.description:
Welcoming Niharika Konidela, a close friend of mine, to this episode of Nikhil Tho Naatakalu 2.0

Niharika Konidela is an Indian actress and producer who predominantly works in the Telugu film industry.

In this video for the first time ever Niharika Konidela opens up about family, career, divorce and politics. 

I hope you enjoy this video, let us know your thoughts in the comments below. 

Thank you Niha for trusting us and coming. You have been a great friend. Wish you all the luck.

(0:00) - Intro
(1:00) -  Adulthood : Friendships &  Money
(12:20) -  Tough times & family
(18:21) - Going through a divorce
(31:50) - Political opinions & Involvement
(37:40) - Love for travel
(40:18) - The producer life
(44:37) - Spirituality & Fitness
(48:30) - Film choices & close family
(54:04) - Dealing with negativity

snippet.description:
Today, in our village, we are cooking a soft layered parotta recipe with mutton gravy baked in banana leaf. 

The Kizhi parotta recipe is very famous in South India, and it is very delicious to eat. Normally, the parotta recipe has a lot of fans so the different types of parotta varieties are comes from the hotels.

snippet.description:
Experience the divine melody of 'Anjanadri,' the soul-stirring Telugu song from the movie HanuMan. Sung by Sai Charan, with music composed by GowraHari and heartfelt lyrics penned by Siva Shakthi Datta, this composition is a celestial journey that resonates with devotion and musical brilliance. üé∂‚ú®

https://youtube.com/TipsTelugu

Singer: Sai Charan Bhaaskaruni 
Music Composed, Arranged & Rhythms Programmed By: GowraHari
Lyrics: Siva Shakthi Datta  
Master : Shadab Rayeen
Mix : GowraHari 
Programming : Ebenezer paul

Movie Details : 
Written and directed by Prasanth Varma
Starring Teja Sajja, Amritha Aiyer, Varalakshmi Sarath Kumar, Vinay Rai, Raj Deepak Shetty, Vennela Kishore, Getup Srinu, Satya etc.,

Anjanadri Pai Santhali Korakai     
Ahoratramulu Thapassu Chese 
Vanara Kesari, Kesari Kulasathi 
Kadupu Pantaga.. Janinchinadoka  
Asamana Baloddhathudu Samyuthudu 
Anjanasuthudu Pavana Nandanudu 
 
Aruna Kiranamula Udayarkuni Gani 
Adhi Pandina Thiyani Pandanukuni Suryamandalamu Patti Thinalani Uvvillure 
Thana Dheham Matuna Ravi Marugai Jagamu Cheekataipoga..  
 

Adhi Amarendrudu Gamaninchi  Thana - Iravathamadhirohinchi Anjaneyuni Samipinchi Thana Vajrayudhamunu Visaraga Adhi Pavana Nandanuni Hanuvuni Thaaka 
 
Chindina Raktha Bindhuve Vidhyuth Vegamtho Dharani Sthali Vanga 
Kadalilo Jocchi 
 
Vanga Kadali, Attaduguna Gala Shree 
Ranga Shukthi Garbhammu Cheri Ata 
Kaalakramamuna Ghanibhavinchi 
Hanumarudhira Mani Ghruniyai 
Arhatha Gala Oka Sahrudhayudikai 
Nirantha Nishchala Nireekshanam

snippet.title: Monkey Man | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Monkey Man 
One small ember can burn down everything. 
#MonkeyManMovie Only in Theaters April 5. 

Oscar¬Æ nominee Dev Patel (Lion, Slumdog Millionaire) achieves an astonishing, tour-de-force feature directing debut with an action thriller about one man‚Äôs quest for vengeance against the corrupt leaders who murdered his mother and continue to systemically victimize the poor and powerless.

Inspired by the legend of Hanuman, an icon embodying strength and courage, Monkey Man stars Patel as Kid, an anonymous young man who ekes out a meager living in an underground fight club where, night after night, wearing a gorilla mask, he is beaten bloody by more popular fighters for cash.

After years of suppressed rage, Kid discovers a way to infiltrate the enclave of the city‚Äôs sinister elite. As his childhood trauma boils over, his mysteriously scarred hands unleash an explosive campaign of retribution to settle the score with the men who took everything from him.

Packed with thrilling and spectacular fight and chase scenes, Monkey Man is directed by Dev Patel from his original story and his screenplay with Paul Angunawela and John Collee (Master and Commander: The Far Side of the World).

The film‚Äôs international cast includes Sharlto Copley (District 9), Sobhita Dhulipala (Made in Heaven), Pitobash (Million Dollar Arm), Vipin Sharma (Hotel Mumbai), Ashwini Kalsekar (Ek Tha Hero), Adithi Kalkunte (Hotel Mumbai), Sikandar Kher (Aarya) and Makarand Deshpande (RRR).

Monkey Man is produced by Dev Patel, Jomon Thomas (Hotel Mumbai, The Man Who Knew Infinity), Oscar¬Æ winner Jordan Peele (Nope, Get Out), Win Rosenfeld (Candyman, Hunters series), Ian Cooper (Nope, Us), Basil Iwanyk (John Wick franchise, Sicario films), Erica Lee (John Wick franchise, Silent Night), Christine Haebler (Shut In, Bones of Crows) and Anjay Nagpal (executive producer of Bombshell, Greyhound). 
 
Serving as executive producers are Jonathan Fuhrman, Natalya Pavchinskya, Aaron L. Gilbert, Andria Spring, Alison-Jane Roney and Steven Thibault.
 
Universal Pictures presents a Bron Studios production, a Thunder Road film, a Monkeypaw production, a Minor Realm/S‚ÄôYa Concept production, in association with WME Independent and Creative Wealth Media.

snippet.title: Best Bike Under 1 Lac - Hero Xtreme 125R First Ride | ICN Studio
snippet.description: Right after its launch at the 2024 Hero World, we got the opportunity to take a quick ride on Hero Xtreme 125R at Hero's test track. Unlike the Splendor 125 and Passion 125, this one is a more premium offering from the brand with modern hardware and a fresh new design. This one targets a rather young set of buyers who want their motorcycle to look sporty and has all the bells and whistles that are otherwise offered in a segment higher motorcycle. It also gets a brand new 125cc engine with a balancer shaft and silent cam chain thus making it pretty smooth to ride. This engine produces a max power output of 10.7PS and 10.6Nm, and is claimed to return a mileage of 66kmpl.

‡∞™‡±ä‡∞§‡±ç‡∞§‡±Å‡∞≤‡∞™‡±à ‡∞ö‡∞Ç‡∞¶‡±ç‡∞∞‡∞¨‡∞æ‡∞¨‡±Å‡∞ï‡±Å ‡∞™‡∞µ‡∞®‡±ç ‡∞ï‡∞≤‡±ç‡∞Ø‡∞æ‡∞£‡±ç ‡∞ú‡∞≤‡∞ï‡±ç || Pawan Kalyan tit for tat to TDP ||

Jana Sena chief Pawan Kalyan declared two Assembly seats from which the party would contest in the coming general elections to the State Assembly. He said that he is announcing the two seats because his ally, the TDP, had announced two seats. He said that He said that when the two parties agreed to go in alliance, the TDP had crossed the rule by declaring two seats. He also found fault with TDP general secretary Nara Lokesh stating that his father N Chandrababu Naidu would be the chief minister. He said he took the statement easily because some sacrifices are to be made when two parties come together. He emphasized the need to defeat Jagan Mohan Reddy in the coming elections. He said that the state would not witness any development if Jagan Mohan Reddy is elected for another term. He wanted to stop Jagan from coming back to power and had tied up with the TDP. He wanted the TDP leaders to restrain from making any statement that would harm the interests of the two parties and their alliance. Pawan Kalyan said that the Jana Sena would contest from Rajam and Rajanagaram Assembly constituencies. He declared this during the Republic Day celebrations and said that he is ready to declare more seats if the TDP also declares their seats. He sought to advise the TDP leaders to stop declaring assembly seats when there is alliance.

Read more at telugu360.com: Pawan declares two seats, invites YSRCP leaders - https://www.telugu360.com/pawan-declares-two-seats-invites-ysrcp-leaders/

In this intriguing case, the CID team delves into the abduction of the wife of a prominent and wealthy businessman. The kidnappers demand a peculiar ransom of 5 crores, to be delivered in 5 instalments at 5 different locations. As CID attempts to unravel this complex and strategic plot, they find themselves consistently outsmarted by the cunning perpetrators. Suspecting the involvement of an insider, CID faces the challenge of identifying the traitor within the businessman's circle. Watch this gripping episode to uncover the twists and turns in the pursuit of the kidnapper.

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
‚Ä¢ Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman

#CID #‡§∏‡•Ä‡§Ü‡§à‡§°‡•Ä #cid2024  #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #Horror #LIVCrime #NewCID #Crime #NewCID #LatestCID

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

As CID attempts to unravel this complex and strategic plot, they find themselves consistently outsmarted by the cunning perpetrators. Suspecting the involvement of an insider, CID faces the challenge of identifying the traitor within the businessman's circle. Watch this gripping episode to uncover the twists and turns in the pursuit of the kidnapper.
